				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Gia-Lu%E1%BA%ADt-S%E1%BB%9F-T%C3%A0i/%C3%82m-S%C6%A1n/poem-ca72WAW3cFoS47O8w34xaw">Âm Sơn - 陰山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gia-Lu%E1%BA%ADt-S%E1%BB%9F-T%C3%A0i/author-hW5UqHVoDIes9sj7tB65qg">Gia Luật Sở Tài</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/Bi%E1%BB%87n-h%C3%A0-%C4%91%C3%ACnh/poem-8w58JoZWGlMEndiXykqYSQ">Biện hà đình - 汴河亭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/author-67u8r1Npo8IzUDBZnVHSFA">Hứa Hồn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-B%E1%BA%A3o-tam-ni%C3%AAn-Nh%C3%A2m-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-khoa-ti%E1%BA%BFn-s%C4%A9-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-danh-k%C3%BD/poem-lmPI_Y7GazogxyWzI82qMg">Đại Bảo tam niên Nhâm Tuất khoa tiến sĩ đề danh ký - 大寶弎年壬戌科進士題名記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/author-eOFIe3QgfrDzlduYauxtuQ">Thân Nhân Trung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Qu%E1%BA%BF/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Thi%C3%AAn-M%E1%BB%A5-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-0WSGy20WoCOZZZBer0Y7bw">Đề Thiên Mụ tự - 題天姥寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Qu%E1%BA%BF/author-tVCgetl94ylIpxXT-wJP2g">Phan Quế</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-T%E1%BA%A5n/%C4%90i%E1%BB%87p-luy%E1%BA%BFn-hoa/poem-Zs9dtyjeea2DYuneWwo4-g">Điệp luyến hoa - 蝶戀花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-ZFmBytLkTH8oyiE6k7djEA">Đào Tấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/Kh%E1%BB%91c-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Kh%C3%AD-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-_GFtvtCfmdcLU-HVPAgQlA">Khốc đệ Ngạn Khí ca kỳ 5 - 哭弟彥器歌其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/author-HrCILDC9soRz0JVGAcDF9w">Lê Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-H%C3%A0m/K%E1%BB%B3-26/poem-yFq7Lsljme7XseeEOeKJEw">Kỳ 26 - 其二十六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-H%C3%A0m/author-FUm0aTv6MMEhKSvKSGMoVA">Vũ Phạm Hàm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%BAc-B%E1%BA%A3o/Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-th%E1%BB%A5-h%E1%BA%ADu-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-hoa/poem-og0yg1YWgltsRxS7PoXrcQ">Ngọc thụ hậu đình hoa - 玉樹後庭花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%BAc-B%E1%BA%A3o/author-ePng4ZVSjzkdkdz3_RrL9w">Trần Thúc Bảo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A3o-Qu%C3%A2n-Huy/Quan-san-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-QFhiUndpGmvB9Yd5ybJ9MA">Quan san nguyệt - 關山月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A3o-Qu%C3%A2n-Huy/author-2hzvu0BiQgKQwJr4CYTN8w">Bảo Quân Huy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Thanh-b%C3%ACnh-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-YGXtqjJz9I3lyd9U9uryRw">Thanh bình điệu kỳ 2 - 清平調其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br></div>	</div>
